sequenceDiagram
    participant SupervisorAI
    participant AgentA
    participant AgentB
    participant DebateEngine
    participant AgentVoting
    participant ContextManager

    SupervisorAI->>DebateEngine: Initiate Debate (Topic, Participating Agents)
    DebateEngine->>AgentA: Request Claims & Evidence
    AgentA-->>DebateEngine: Claims & Evidence
    DebateEngine->>AgentB: Request Claims & Evidence
    AgentB-->>DebateEngine: Claims & Evidence

    loop Debate Rounds
        DebateEngine->>AgentA: Request Counterarguments/Rebuttals
        AgentA-->>DebateEngine: Counterarguments/Rebuttals
        DebateEngine->>AgentB: Request Counterarguments/Rebuttals
        AgentB-->>DebateEngine: Counterarguments/Rebuttals
        DebateEngine->>DebateEngine: Evaluate Arguments, Confidence, Sources
    end

    DebateEngine->>AgentVoting: Request Vote (Decision Options, Agent Confidence)
    AgentVoting->>AgentA: Cast Vote
    AgentA-->>AgentVoting: Vote (Option, Confidence)
    AgentVoting->>AgentB: Cast Vote
    AgentB-->>AgentVoting: Vote (Option, Confidence)
    AgentVoting->>AgentVoting: Apply Voting Mechanism (Weighted, Majority, etc.)
    AgentVoting-->>DebateEngine: Voting Result (Consensus, Tie, etc.)

    DebateEngine->>DebateEngine: Final Synthesis
    DebateEngine-->>SupervisorAI: Debate Outcome (Decision, Explanation, Supporting Evidence)
    SupervisorAI->>ContextManager: Record Debate Outcome & Audit Trail
    ContextManager-->>SupervisorAI: Confirmation
